Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all because of my misjudgment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel bad for you all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I want to make sure\Nto wipe out all those squirts now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the Third Laboratory, there \Nis another weapon that was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:28.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,responsible for destroying the \NFirst and Second Laboratory{\i0}
