Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I met him at a garbage dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought him with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eel is gonna attack me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this dragon? He said "Father."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find out later.
