Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Transponder Snail \Nstill receiving the signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like there was an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was in D Building.
