Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Smoker!
