Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can get out of here,\Nwe'll go separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is something \NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
