Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Caesar had my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it end up in your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me keep your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's a deal!
