Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave his secretary Monet's heart \Nback to him out of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respond.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As they say, if you are kind to people,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,good things will happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you like it?\NThis Missile Girl's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...flame of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Baby 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need this weapon?\NEven though you're a weapon woman yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for picking it up, Buffalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my good luck charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An owner of this weapon is \Ndestined to become happy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if you buy this, \Nyou'd make me happy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...needs me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely sure that he fooled you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:17:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm an invincible Iron Pirate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't fight for the peace of the sea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Iron Pirate!\N--How persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapon-morphosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revolver Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just made me itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's pretty tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Buffalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good!\NIt's collapsing faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The passage is gonna collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a tunnel through a mountain.\NIf it collapses, we'll be buried alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it in a relaxed matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! The wreckage blocked our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the brakes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe it! He saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to be my enemy!\NAlthough he already is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too comfortable yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadly gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:20:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that thing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it flowing in through \Ncracks of walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be more than \Njust being buried alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying such horrible things\Nin a cool manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is going to be \Ngas around the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can anybody here generate wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so easy to find a person\Nwith such a special skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How easy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:21:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:22:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Young Master is nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be in the room \Non the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh! He wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The window was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I don't know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.45,0:22:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went out by himself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Tell me what's \Ngoing on over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-We've actually been blocked by\Nsome kind of iron guard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it still safe there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, it is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the island and those squirts\Nhaven't been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:23:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of that guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way!
